    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Originally referred to buildings that house banks with offices or branches located in vehicles that may be set up in changing locations. The term more recently refers to buildings that house banks that allow financial transactions to be made over mobile devices, such as a cell phone.</Note_Text>
